Package com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.task

Class TaskDto

java.lang.Object
com.ilm.projecto_ilm_backend.dto.task.TaskDto
public class TaskDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object for representing a task. This class encapsulates details about a task, including its ID, title, system title, description, status, project state, initial and final dates, out collaboration status, dependent tasks, and members of the task.
